      "12c0fdb9-b7f2-4996-9f00-300058f745cf"]
    }], "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"50d61a47-91e8-4e4e-8800-52fa57ef7d34"], 
    Cell["the list of input / output qudit dimensions of the circuit", 
