the picture of the circuit (e.g. Schrodinger, Heisenberg or PhaseSpace)\
\>", "TableText",ExpressionUUID->"efe99e61-647a-4d4a-8cde-8935acc523f1"]},
   {Cell["      ", "ModInfo",ExpressionUUID->
     "eb558f9e-fe6f-4f6a-a598-4f77a5f1a7b3"], Cell[TextData[Cell[
