Cell["\<\
Given the result of the above circuit, find the corresponding amplitudes and \
normalize them to get the HHL solution:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"7ad0ad4d-b258-4e8a-a2ae-d0f2f47b5755"],

